d":1631981,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:27.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"4b5344bd47dcd9d85c98e26e9b81abc7f7785da2","tid":1631981,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"1cd681780860bfc268900bc292daf9edaa1be451","tid":1631981,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"42a5e9c93767f3911ef21a83a7908a294bc15c7c","tid":1631981,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:30.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"57a4a099dadc8d651268c6c7007d4f656159432a","tid":1631981,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"[行動Post] 請大家今晚開始穩固返好文宣戰線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631997</a>"},{"pid":"ff929e91d926ef34dcbd9f44a0115e1bdf8b99cd","tid":1631981,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57a4a099dadc8d651268c6c7007d4f656159432a","tid":1631981,"uid":49781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"[行動Post] 請大家今晚開始穩固返好文宣戰線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631997</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"重要, 推"},{"pid":"6fe8da4f2122381fd22f470611dadd103aa96893","tid":1631981,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5d35ec9768329dfce156919972d319a8cd17e92","tid":1631981,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:43:37.000Z","msg":"1) 一係一日全和, 一日全勇<br />\n和果日全部扮街坊, 要人多, 純粹比記者+國際影相, 狗挑釁即閃。可分區, 可